The fatalities of six Emirati soldiers in the SAM incident date : 13-09-2019 09-2019 03 : 36 : 19 Battles : 1572 National Yum-Oman : The General Command of the UAE Armed Forces announced the deaths of six of its soldiers as a result of an accident involving the destruction of military mechanisms that dispensed their national patents in the ground of operations , and are Captain Sabad Rashid al-Mansuri . Agents Ol Ali Abdullah Abdallah Shahani .